<template>
  
</template>
<script>
import axios from 'axios'
export default {
  name: "MyAccount",
  methods: {
    logout() {
      axios.defaults.headers.common["Authorization"] = ""
      localStorage.removeItem("token")
      localStorage.removeItem("username")
      localStorage.removeItem("")
    }
  }
}
</script>
